name: Wavy
description: Wavy is like that point when all of the drugs in your body are working togetherrrrr, as in unified and concentrated into one ultimate serotonin drop of perfection. A place where you are invincible but vulnerable but none of that EVEN MATTERS because what you are experiencing in the here and now is you me them US and the USNESS is just one thing just one US so how can anything even matter? Just laid back and immaculate, spreading infinite.
